a6cb3743408b9bf8caac09e993375a08211bc7e8e9fb&"}, {"id": "1252194653281718272", "filename": "Screenshot_20240617_173339.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 139492, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1252194651037896795/1252194653281718272/Screenshot_20240617_173339.jpg?ex=69cb9525&is=69ca43a5&hm=3deba7aadda3faa741e3a9c7e9e58ba102250fa6295d59d6543cdd9570038bf7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252194651037896795", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "350溶災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1252316432117796915", "channel_id": "1252194651037896795", "type": 0, "author_id": "1122207553053528217", "author_name": "yi000607", "author_bot": false, "content": "1-3 提高爆擊暴傷完全適合羅坦，我的練度還不算高技能也都沒拉滿，不然1-4應該也是輕輕鬆鬆\n\n2-3會給+70狂氣的牌，適合24上場，我24也是超低練度\n\n3-4 要小心的點是盡量不要讓24 高爆發的傷害直接打到臉上，不然神父的回血效率會直接裂開，平常我不會覺醒神父，但為了擋二階段第一發爆發所以選擇覺醒，\n另外我為了不要浪費菲的狂氣爆發效果，選擇在某一次24高爆發的時候送第一次死抗，一方面可以讓菲繼續加死抗，也能讓菲3費效益更高。\n只要第一階段熬過其實第二階段很容易過，救救我盡量留到二階24爆發時使用", "timestamp": "2024-06-17T17:38:24.331000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252194651037896795", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "350溶災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1252316875702927483", "channel_id": "1252194651037896795", "type": 0, "author_id": "1122207553053528217", "author_name": "yi000607", "author_bot": false, "content": "4-2\n超低練度深海 根本沒在練，反正-2的都很簡單沒有甚麼技巧\n\n5-3 適合尤烏 24這種，在一階段把傷害疊起來，二階段秒掉，有加侖解遲緩會更舒服", "timestamp": "2024-06-17T17:40:10.090000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-17T17:40:23.606000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1252194651037896795", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "350溶災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
